   44     | factor

   45 factor: NEGOP factor
   46       | exponent

   47 exponent: primary EXPOP exponent
   48         | primary

   49 primary: '(' expression ')'
   50        | INT_LITERAL
   51        | CHAR_LITERAL
   52        | REAL_LITERAL
   53        | IDENTIFIER '(' expression ')'
   54        | IDENTIFIER


